    <div class="col-md-4">
        <p>Guidelines for posts</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Please try to rhyme.</li>
            <li>Not using the letter "A" will save you time.</li>
            <li>Using numerous hashtags will get you banned, and cost you a dime. </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { topic: @topic, post: @post } %>
    </div>
</div>